{"_path":"/maps/_industry/analytics","_dir":"_industry","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"行业报告","description":"行业研究、分析、报告等","original_path":"content/6.maps/_industry/analytics.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.idc.com/resource-center","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"IDC Analyst Insights"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"美国人对外星人和神秘生物的信仰调查"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"美国人对外星人和神秘生物的信仰调查"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"YouGov 对 1,114 名美国成年人的调查显示，相信超自然存在的人数可能超出预期。\n超过半数美国人（56%）相信外星人存在，其中 18% 绝对相信、38% 可能相信。\n相比之下，神秘生物的信仰率较低：大脚怪（28%）、雪人（23%）、尼斯湖水怪（22%）、卓柏卡布拉（16%）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.visualcapitalist.com/cp/who-believes-in-aliens-bigfoot-and-the-chupacabra/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Who Believes in Aliens, Bigfoot, and the Chupacabra?"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"美国食品安全food-insecurity州级分布调查"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"美国食品安全（Food Insecurity）州级分布调查"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"USDA 对 32,719 户家庭的调查显示（2022-2024 年数据），美国各州食品不安全率存在显著地区差异。\n全国平均为 13.3%，但南部多州远高于此水平。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"食品不安全（Food Insecurity）是指由于经济资源有限，无法持续获得足够营养食物的状态。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最高："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 阿肯色州（19.4%）、肯塔基州（18.8%）、路易斯安那州（17.7%）\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最低："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 北达科他州（9.0%）、新罕布什尔州（9.1%）、佛蒙特州（9.4%）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"值得注意的是，德州和加州虽然比率不同（17.6% vs 12.5%），但因人口庞大，影响的家庭数量均超过千万户。\n食品不安全与低收入、高贫困率、农村人口多、依赖公共援助等结构性经济因素密切相关。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.visualcapitalist.com/food-security-is-highest-state-by-state/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Where Food Insecurity Is Highest, State by State"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"各国麦当劳人均拥有量地图"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"各国麦当劳人均拥有量地图"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"麦当劳在全球近 100 个市场拥有超过 40,000 家门店。\n按人均计算，澳门（56.8 家/百万人）和圣马丁（43.2 家/百万人）领先，美国以 38.6 家/百万人位居大型国家之首。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"亚洲差异显著："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 尽管中印人口都超过 14 亿，但中国人均拥有量（约 5 家/百万人）是印度（0.5 家）的 10 倍；日本（24.1 家）与巴基斯坦（0.3 家，全球最低）差距更大。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"市场潜力："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 非洲仅有埃及、摩洛哥、南非三个国家设有麦当劳门店；中东地区卡塔尔（27.6 家）和以色列（23.1 家）密度较高。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"退出市场："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2022 年麦当劳全面退出俄罗斯（850 家门店），2024 年出售斯里兰卡全部 12 家门店。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.visualcapitalist.com/mapped-how-many-mcdonalds-each-country-has-per-person/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mapped: The Countries With the Most McDonald's Per Person"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"北极冰层流失可视化1980-2025"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"北极冰层流失可视化（1980-2025）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NASA 数据显示，自 1980 年以来北极夏季海冰以每十年 12.2% 的速度缩小。\n1980 年至 2025 年间，北极最小冰范围减少了 110 万平方英里（约 280 万平方公里），相当于阿根廷的国土面积。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"按当前趋势，北极可能在 2050 年夏季出现\"几乎无冰\"状态。\n这一变化正在打开新的全球航运路线——北方海路可比苏伊士运河缩短近 20 天航程（约 40%）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地缘政治影响："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 北极估计拥有 4120 亿桶未发现石油和大量稀土资源（格陵兰储量全球第八）。中国、俄罗斯、美国、欧盟均已制定北极国家战略，该地区正成为新的地缘政治竞争焦点。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.visualcapitalist.com/arctic-ice-loss-compared-to-the-size-of-countries/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Visualizing Arctic Ice Loss Since 1980, Compared to Countries"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"海洋未来探索蓝色经济投资机遇"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海洋未来探索：蓝色经济投资机遇"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与迪拜未来论坛合作的研究显示，海洋正成为新的投资前沿。\n尽管海洋覆盖地球 70% 以上，但仅 27% 的海底被现代标准测绘，剩余 73% 的未测绘面积比所有陆地面积还大。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"生物多样性潜力巨大："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 估计 91% 的海洋生物尚未被发现，目前已知约 34.7 万种。每年科学家都能发现和编目数千个新物种，这些发现可能为医药和技术突破提供线索。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"蓝色经济投资："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2010-2023 年海洋相关投资翻倍，摩根士丹利预计未来将产生超过 3 万亿美元的投资机会："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海洋运输脱碳：1.2 万亿美元"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海洋生态系统保护：1.1 万亿美元"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可再生能源：8400 亿美元"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"tex